  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\n\n- [X] Foundry\n- [X] Foundryup\n\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\n\nforge 0.2.0 (d4c615b 2022-03-24T01:05:20.744764+00:00)\n\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\n\nforge clean\n\n### Operating System\n\nmacOS (M1)\n\n### Describe the bug\n\nRunning forge clean should just clear the out and cache directories when default settings are used but the artifacts directory is additionally deleted.  See below\r\n![foundry_artifact_bug](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8229664/160250612-91191ebe-adce-41e1-906e-08ff68db8388.jpg)",
